                <p className="text-gaming-gray">Deploy your own server with this exact control panel in under 60 seconds.</p>
              </div>
              <Link href="/games">
                <Button className="bg-gaming-green text-gaming-black hover:bg-gaming-green-dark font-semibold">
                  Get Started Today
